&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; o Service returns<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; o Production failures that pass our existing fixtures.<br />
&bull; Create HW test plans as required and review test data.<br />
&bull; Perform HW analysis and create reports.<br />
&bull; Create reports for feedback of HW issues to new designs.<br />
&bull; Create SW/test SW as necessary for HW validation<br />
&bull; Generate engineering documents: specifications, schematics, BOM, validation reports, schedules etc.<br />
