			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Midtronics has an opening for a full time Service Technician in the Transportation Department.&nbsp; The Service Technician will be responsible for troubleshooting, repairing, testing, and calibrating products returned from customers due to warranty claims and/or time and material repairs.&nbsp; The technician must have the ability to disassemble the units, identify the problem, replace defective parts, and document the outcome on an RMA form.&nbsp; The technician must be able to perform these functions, including repackaging the product for return.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
